STATE of Washington, Respondent,
v.
Daniel Herbert DUNBAR, Petitioner. No. 96801-2 Supreme Court of Washington. DATED at Olympia, Washington, May 8, 2019.

ORDER

¶ 1 Department I of the Court, composed of Chief Justice Fairhurst and Justices Johnson, Owens, Wiggins and Gordon McCloud, considered this matter at its April 30, 2019, Motion Calendar and entered an order continuing this matter to the June 6, 2019, En Banc Conference. After further consideration of this matter, the Department unanimously agreed that the following order be entered.

¶ 2 IT IS ORDERED:

¶ 3 That the petition for review is denied.

For the Court

/s/ Fairhurst, C.J.

CHIEF JUSTICE
